    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290090/extras/6e59cf6872718d8aee5f627bec384aae.avif?t=1741971931\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Absolution is a first-person visual novel. In the eerie depths of this psychological thriller, face THE JUDGE and a twisted tale of grief, guilt and murder. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Confront your sins. Reflect on your morals. Liars will be punished.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290090/extras/09227482e0ab096edcc0781705ec247d.avif?t=1741971931\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Horror Experience</strong>: Come immerse yourself in an experience that blends eerie visuals with haunting soundscapes as an unnerving story unveils before you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unnerving Questions</strong>: Answer THE JUDGE’s probing questions, where honesty is key—liars will be punished.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chilling Narrative</strong>: Witness the unraveling of a tale filled with desperation, guilt, and the lingering hope for redemption.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Compelling Characters</strong>: Meet the characters of this horrific story. Can they be saved from their fatal fates?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290090/extras/1b62531bb23e1e60b735cd3b13080a41.avif?t=1741971931\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Absolution was developed within the University of Southern California's Games Program. For more information about the USC Games Program, check out their website.</p></li></ul>",
